measurements.description: Forty-seven pristine flowers and nine buds on 30 up to 12-cm inflorescences; immaculate well grown 27-cm x 25-cm plant mounted on 9-cm x 15-cm cork slab; dorsal sepal white, cauda light gold, pronounced raised mid-rib; lateral sepals and caudae light gold; petals and caudae light gold fading to light green centrally; lip white, nectary 9.3-cm, pale green, pale gold distally; substance firm; texture satin; also received award 20235367.
